@startuml
title Enterprise Integration and Agent Runtime Flow

actor User
participant "AI Orchestrator" as Orchestrator
participant "AI Platform Kernel" as Kernel
participant "AI Agent Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Agent Executor" as Executor
participant "Tool" as Tool
participant "AI Integration Service" as Integration
participant "Connector" as Connector
database "Enterprise Resource" as Resource

User -> Orchestrator: submit request
Orchestrator -> Kernel: resolve capability / runtime state
Kernel -> Gateway: execution request
Gateway -> Executor: route execution
Executor -> Tool: invoke tool
Tool -> Integration: integration request
Integration -> Connector: technical call
Connector -> Resource: read/write data
Resource --> Connector: response
Connector --> Integration: normalized response
Integration --> Tool: result
Tool --> Executor: tool result
Executor --> Gateway: execution response
Gateway --> Orchestrator: normalized result
Orchestrator --> User: final answer
@enduml
